1. painlessmesh library installation
2. choose namedmesh example in painlessmesh library
3. wait for D5 gpio status change in ESP8266
4. select proper namedmesh server node

ESP8266 (meshnodes door clients)		     ESP8266 (mesh master)			ESP8266 (Connected to internet)
	|				---->   	|				---->		|
     RF module (Tx node, event)			     RF module(Rx Node, Tx node)		RF module (Rx Node, send to gmail)

5. https://how2electronics.com/esp8266-nrf24l01-gateway-arduino-node/#:~:text=On%20the%20receiver%20end%2C%20we,via%20the%20NRF24L01%20transceiver%20module.
